{%- comment -%}
  moromisu.css は main-page-moromisu.liquid で読み込んでいます
{%- endcomment -%}
<style>
  .c-reasons__inner {
    background: url('{{ 'moromisu-three-reason-bg.png' | asset_url }}') repeat center center;
  }
</style>

<section class="c-reasons">
  <div class="c-reasons__inner">
    <div class="c-reasons__heading">
      <div class="c-reasons__heading-line1">毎日に、無理なく。</div>
      <div class="c-reasons__heading-line2">
        <span>続けやすい</span>
        <span class="c-reasons__heading-num">3</span>
        <span>つの理由</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="c-reasons__sp-hero">
      <div class="c-reasons__hero-image">
        <picture>
          {% if section.settings.mobile_image != blank %}
            <source media="(max-width: 767px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.mobile_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}">
          {% endif %}
          {% if section.settings.pc_image != blank %}
            {{ section.settings.pc_image | image_url: width: 1800 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
          {% elsif section.settings.mobile_image != blank %}
            {{ section.settings.mobile_image | image_url: width: 1200 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
          {% endif %}
        </picture>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="c-reasons__content">
      <div class="c-reasons__layout">
        <div class="c-reasons__list">
          <div class="c-reasons__item">
            <div class="c-reasons__item-header">
              <div class="c-reasons__item-number">1</div>
              <h3 class="c-reasons__item-title">まろやかで飲みやすい味わい</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="c-reasons__item-desc">
              <p>"酢"と名がついていますが、酢酸が主成分である食酢や黒酢とは異なり、もろみ酢の主成分はクエン酸とアミノ酸。<br>他の酢と比べて匂いやツンとくる酸味が少なく、まろやかな風味が特長です。毎日飲んでも負担になりにくく、「続けること」そのものがストレスになりません。</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="c-reasons__item">
            <div class="c-reasons__item-header">
              <div class="c-reasons__item-number">2</div>
              <h3 class="c-reasons__item-title">食事にプラスするだけの手軽さ</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="c-reasons__item-desc">
              <p>特別な準備は不要。朝食や食後、リラックスタイムなど、いつもの生活に一杯加えるだけ。忙しい日々でも、無理なく取り入れられ、習慣にしやすいのが魅力です。</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="c-reasons__item">
            <div class="c-reasons__item-header">
              <div class="c-reasons__item-number">3</div>
              <h3 class="c-reasons__item-title">体にうれしい成分を一度に摂れる</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="c-reasons__item-desc">
              <p>お米・黒麹・酵母の発酵によって、体内で合成できない「必須アミノ酸」9種類を含む18種類以上のアミノ酸や、クエン酸などの栄養を豊富に含有。</p>
              <p>「いろいろ気にせず、これ一本」というシンプルさが、継続につながります。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="c-reasons__images">
          <div class="c-reasons__hero-image">
            <picture>
              {% if section.settings.mobile_image != blank %}
                <source media="(max-width: 767px)" srcset="{{ section.settings.mobile_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}">
              {% endif %}
              {% if section.settings.pc_image != blank %}
                {{ section.settings.pc_image | image_url: width: 1800 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
              {% elsif section.settings.mobile_image != blank %}
                {{ section.settings.mobile_image | image_url: width: 1200 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
              {% endif %}
            </picture>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Moromisu Three Reasons",
  "class": "shopify-section--main-page-moromisu",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "もろみ酢LPページでの利用を想定しています"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "pc_image",
      "label": "PC画像"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "mobile_image",
      "label": "Mobile画像"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Moromisu Three Reasons"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
